These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, tea
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: july, november
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: marigold, poppy
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: disco, soul
The people use 2 different means of transport: tram, boat
2 different games are played: snooker, mah-jongg
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: disaster, thriller
1. the person playing snooker is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3
2. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
3. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
4. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
5. the person watching thriller movies is the person who growspoppy##1
6. the fan of soul is the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |
| Beverage      | tea        | hot-chocolate |
| Birthday          | november  | july     |
| Flower         | poppy    | marigold         |
| Music-Genre           | disco    | soul |
| Transport   | tram  | boat     |
| Game           | mah-jongg      | snooker    |
| Movie-Genre         | thriller | disaster          |

